  • Method Details

    • parse

      public PropertyMap parse()
      Return PropertyMap of packet en PacketPath. Note this PropertyMap is a AbstractLockablePropertyMap and AbstractLockablePropertyMap.lock() is call. So this map is immutable.
      Returns:
      propertymap who contain in key a packet name and in value (only) PacketPath of target key

    • add

      private boolean add​(String file, PropertyMap map, String suffix, String path, int treeLevel, JsonElement element)
      Add all detected packets in a PropertyMap. This walk in every sub section of JsonObject is element is JsonObject
      Parameters:
      file - target file
      map - PropertyMap where put result
      suffix - in/out
      path - current path
      treeLevel - current level (s1.s2.s3 has a treeLevel of 3)
      element - current JsonElement
      Returns:
      true if add is a success and false else
